This is the code used to build http://ubuntudanmark.dk/

HOW TO INSTALL
Place files in web root.
Open site in browser and compleate WordPress installation.
Activate Ubuntu thme in WordPress.
Download phpBB 3.0.10 and extract config.php and the install folder to the forum folder.
Browse to /forum/ and compleate the phpBB installation.
Activate PHP SSO in WordPress.
In phpBB admin go to Server Configuration->Security and set Allow php in templates to yes.
Activate Ubuntu theme in phpBB.
Go to Appearance->Menus and create a new menu with a custome link for /forum/.
Go to widgits and add the menu.
